     H            Y.
     F** UEXR29E ********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: GET EDI PARTNER ID BY DELIVERY#           *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA) 2025.05.02                       *
     F*-----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UEXR29E'
     F*                    PARM           $NONY   4
     F*                    PARM           $PRTN  30
     F*  IN  $NONY :  4A DELIVERY#
     F*  OUT $PRTN : 30A EDI PERTNER ID
     F******************************************************
     FAB#EP01 IF  E           K        DISK
      *===================================================
      *           MAIN ROUTINE
      *===================================================
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $NONY   4
     C                     PARM           $PRTN  30
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $PRTN
      * GET FROM AB#EP01
     C                     MOVEL$NONY     @@NONY  40
     C           @@NONY    CHAINAB#EP01              98
     C           *IN98     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVELEP1PRT    $PRTN
     C                     GOTO ENDP
     C                     ENDIF
      * FOR HONDA
     C           $PRTN     IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     EXSR #HONDA
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           ENDP      TAG
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      *===================================================
      * GET HONDA
      *===================================================
     C           #HONDA    BEGSR
     C                     ENDSR
